 - Be even more precise

```
type Key = &#39;key1&#39; | &#39;key2&#39; | &#39;key3&#39; | &#39;key4&#39;
var keys: Key[] = [&#39;key1&#39;, &#39;key2&#39;, &#39;key3&#39;, &#39;key4&#39;]
